USAGE: gnrt --movie-nfo [-o \"outfile\"]
       gnrt --movie-nfo -h

NOTE:


EXAMPLE:
  FILE NAME: "Justice League.nfo"

  FILE CONTENT:
    <?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes" ?>
    <movie>
